NAME
    App::PDRUtils - Collection of utilities for perl dist repos

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.120 of App::PDRUtils (from Perl
    distribution App-PDRUtils), released on 2018-04-03.

SYNOPSIS
    This distribution provides the following command-line utilities related
    to perl dist repos:

    *   pdrutil

    *   pdrutil-multi

DESCRIPTION
    If you have one or more CPAN (or DarkPAN) perl distribution repos on
    your filesystem, then this suite of CLI utilities might be useful for
    you. Currently only the combination of Dist::Zilla-based Perl
    distributions managed by git version control is supported.

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/App-PDRUtils>.

SOURCE
    Source repository is at
    <https://github.com/perlancar/perl-App-PDRUtils>.

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests on the bugtracker website
    <https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Dist/Display.html?Name=App-PDRUtils>

    When submitting a bug or request, please include a test-file or a patch
    to an existing test-file that illustrates the bug or desired feature.

